    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_jc.00202_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden  NJ  US America</name>
                    <date when="1888-07-23">Monday Evn'g  July 23 '88<ptr target="loc.03840_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute/>
            </opener>

            <p>Thanks first for your good letter rec'd to day&#8212;I am better than the long obstinate
                siege (nearly six weeks) would warrant&#8212;I am sitting here at my booklet proofs <hi rend="underline">Nov:
                    Boughs</hi>&#8212;(only two or three days now have I felt the grip on my poor brain)&#8212;I almost
                envy your Wales fun&#8212;Love to you and Mary<ptr target="loc.02189_n1"/> &#38; all&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <salute/>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_jc.00201_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
